{
  "stem": "13382.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No alcohol.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "For everybody.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Not for the Jews, because that was-- and they came in to celebrate with the two girls as it was a lull-- lull evening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So the caretaker's flat was still reasonable condition.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they went into the caretaker's flat, into one room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Wine drinking and singing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And while it was all [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I came up with those three--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we settled ourselves in the kitchen, kitchen table, and take out cards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we start to play cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bang on the door later [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was a [INAUDIBLE] guard, which was the [INAUDIBLE] part of the Hungary patrol hearing the music and voices as they came in, and they wanted to check what's happening.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After all, it's martial law.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How can they [? see? ?]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came into the kitchen, and one Jewish boy and the other, you know, is sitting at the table.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this-- this should not be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I mean, we all would sort of-- would have been executed on the spot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the leader of the [? things, ?] he asked me, what that music and-- and singing?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, they are our German brothers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So before he went into [INAUDIBLE], I would like to see them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Before he went in, I met one of the Germans who was quite friend-- a good friend of mine and tell him in German, listen, my friend.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are after these-- you and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, I would suggest that you take-- take a glass of-- and a bottle of wine and give that bottle of wine to the leader and ask him to drink and not to-- not to bother us.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
